sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Customer
    participant Mu as MultiSafepay
    participant A as Alipay+
    participant Me as Merchant

    C->>Mu: Selects Alipay+ at checkout
    alt Redirect flow
    Mu->>C: Redirects to payment page
    else Direct flow
    Mu->>A: Sends payment request
    end
    A->>Mu: Returns QR code
    Mu->>C: Displays QR code
    C->>A: Scans QR, selects wallet, and completes payment
    A->>Mu: Transfers funds 
    Mu->>Me: Settles funds
	